{"_id":"BrunaThePoorWitc","name":"Bruna the Poor Witch - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Bruna the Poor Witch","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a poor old woman to whom life has \noffered only suffering. Sometimes I manifest strange powers, \nbut I have always concealed this ability out of fear of ending \nup at the stake.</p>","notes":"Bloodwhite's Heart - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 113.","positive":"I am a poor old woman to whom life has \noffered only suffering. Sometimes I manifest strange powers, \nbut I have always concealed this ability out of fear of ending \nup at the stake.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Bruna the Poor Witch","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":400000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557628565,"modifiedTime":1781557628565,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"BellaSServants04","name":"Bella’s Servants - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Bella’s Servants","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>We are young people in the service of Bella \nand we are trained to defend the House \nof Roses.</p>","notes":"The House of Roses - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 127.","positive":"We are young people in the service of Bella \nand we are trained to defend the House \nof Roses.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Bella’s Servants","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":500000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557629804,"modifiedTime":1781557629804,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"AleksandrPtak05x","name":"Aleksandr Pták - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Aleksandr Pták","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am divided between who I was before and \nthe spirit who took possession of my body. I have the urge to \nkill, but since my mind is clouded, I don’t always know why.\nSwallow’s</p>","notes":"I Will Stay with You Always - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 173.","positive":"I am divided between who I was before and \nthe spirit who took possession of my body. I have the urge to \nkill, but since my mind is clouded, I don’t always know why.\nSwallow’s","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Aleksandr Pták","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":600000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557637920,"modifiedTime":1781557637920,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"ArneTheCaptain06","name":"Arne the Captain - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Arne the Captain","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I once was a military man and I’ve earned the \ncrown’s respect. Now, as a ship’s captain, I serve my country and \nboast about my crew.</p>","notes":"Hunger Island - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 95.","positive":"I once was a military man and I’ve earned the \ncrown’s respect. Now, as a ship’s captain, I serve my country and \nboast about my crew.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Arne the Captain","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":700000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557626239,"modifiedTime":1781557626239,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"MercenaryAndRese","name":"Mercenary and Researcher of Renowned Fame - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Mercenary and Researcher of Renowned Fame","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a skilled adventurer and treasure hunter, \nand I have no qualms about doing what it takes to get what \nI want.</p>","notes":"Stegeborg's Quiet - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 139.","positive":"I am a skilled adventurer and treasure hunter, \nand I have no qualms about doing what it takes to get what \nI want.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Mercenary and Researcher of Renowned Fame","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":800000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557636228,"modifiedTime":1781557636228,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"SealOfTheCauldro","name":"Seal of the Cauldron Fae - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Seal of the Cauldron Fae","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>A magic seal capable of manifesting the magic \nof the Cauldron Fae.</p>","notes":"I Don't Believe - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 84.","positive":"A magic seal capable of manifesting the magic \nof the Cauldron Fae.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Seal of the Cauldron Fae","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":900000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557625638,"modifiedTime":1781557625638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"AltheaTheAgentOf","name":"Althea the Agent of the Order - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Althea the Agent of the Order","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a nun in the service of the Order and, \ndespite my ecclesiastical background, I have skills as a spy and \na fighter. The Order entrusts me with high-risk tasks because \nit has confidence in my unwavering faith and ruthlessness.</p>","notes":"Hunger Island - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 99.","positive":"I am a nun in the service of the Order and, \ndespite my ecclesiastical background, I have skills as a spy and \na fighter. The Order entrusts me with high-risk tasks because \nit has confidence in my unwavering faith and ruthlessness.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Althea the Agent of the Order","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":1000000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557626372,"modifiedTime":1781557626372,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"TaliaTheSleeper1","name":"Talia the Sleeper - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a young girl put to sleep for eternity by the \nmagic of Carabosse. The whole castle responds to my will and, \nthanks to my powers, I can see and hear everything.</p>","notes":"Stegeborg's Quiet - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 143.","positive":"I am a young girl put to sleep for eternity by the \nmagic of Carabosse. The whole castle responds to my will and, \nthanks to my powers, I can see and hear everything.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Talia the Sleeper","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":1100000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557636357,"modifiedTime":1781557636357,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"TheCountAzulOfVi","name":"The Count Azul of Vigo - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Count Azul of Vigo","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a rich and bored nobleman who \ncares only about social position.</p>","notes":"In Your Eyes, with Your Feet - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 154.","positive":"I am a rich and bored nobleman who \ncares only about social position.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Count Azul of Vigo","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":1200000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557636919,"modifiedTime":1781557636919,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"OstromirMaly12xx","name":"Ostromir Malý - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Ostromir Malý","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I rule Prague on behalf of Empress Maria \nTheresa and, after the failed siege, I hold the city’s fate in the \npalm of my hand. The recent murders are complicating my \nlife, though so far the noble families support my authority.</p>","notes":"I Will Stay with You Always - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 166.","positive":"I rule Prague on behalf of Empress Maria \nTheresa and, after the failed siege, I hold the city’s fate in the \npalm of my hand. The recent murders are complicating my \nlife, though so far the noble families support my authority.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Ostromir Malý","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":1300000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557637466,"modifiedTime":1781557637466,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"NatureRisesUp13x","name":"Nature Rises Up - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Nature Rises Up","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>Navigating inside the lair without the consent of the Cauldron Fae \nexposes the intruders to the ire of the many plants. Ivy tentacles and pollen mists rise to \nblock those who walk without their lady’s approval.\nMtyrya the Fairy also called the \nCauldron Fae</p>","notes":"I Don't Believe - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 85.","positive":"Navigating inside the lair without the consent of the Cauldron Fae \nexposes the intruders to the ire of the many plants. Ivy tentacles and pollen mists rise to \nblock those who walk without their lady’s approval.\nMtyrya the Fairy also called the \nCauldron Fae","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Nature Rises Up","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":1400000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557625700,"modifiedTime":1781557625700,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"FranciscaAndMart","name":"Francisca and Marta the Vengeful Sisters - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Francisca and Marta the Vengeful Sisters","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>We are two poor sisters sewn together in one \nbody. We move with perfect coordination and cooperate \neffortlessly, each aiding the other against any danger.</p>","notes":"In Your Eyes, with Your Feet - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 157.","positive":"We are two poor sisters sewn together in one \nbody. We move with perfect coordination and cooperate \neffortlessly, each aiding the other against any danger.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Francisca and Marta the Vengeful Sisters","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":1500000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557637117,"modifiedTime":1781557637117,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"PietroGonsalvaRe","name":"Pietro Gonsalva Regent of Capodimonte - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Pietro Gonsalva Regent of Capodimonte","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a rich and powerful nobleman, and I have \nmanaged to ingratiate myself with the Papal State. I love being \nin charge, but over time I’ve learned to trust those who are more \nexperienced than I am.</p>","notes":"The House of Roses - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 125.","positive":"I am a rich and powerful nobleman, and I have \nmanaged to ingratiate myself with the Papal State. I love being \nin charge, but over time I’ve learned to trust those who are more \nexperienced than I am.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Pietro Gonsalva Regent of Capodimonte","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":1600000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557629741,"modifiedTime":1781557629741,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"CernobogPotmesil","name":"Cernobog Potmešil The Child - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cernobog Potmešil The Child","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>The rubies I received allowed me to recover \nfrom the fever that had plagued me and, thanks to them, I \nam now strong and healthy, but at what price? I feel anger \nand resentment towards those who live on the shoulders of \nthe poor people of Prague.</p>","notes":"I Will Stay with You Always - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 173.","positive":"The rubies I received allowed me to recover \nfrom the fever that had plagued me and, thanks to them, I \nam now strong and healthy, but at what price? I feel anger \nand resentment towards those who live on the shoulders of \nthe poor people of Prague.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Cernobog Potmešil The Child","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":1700000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557637921,"modifiedTime":1781557637921,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Lisbet17xxxxxxxx","name":"Lisbet - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Lisbet","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a young widow and I settled in the village \nto start anew. I have experienced many misfortunes in my life, \nwhich have forced me to become stubborn and strong-willed. \nHowever, I’ve managed to stay kind and generous.</p>","notes":"Stegeborg's Quiet - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 143.","positive":"I am a young widow and I settled in the village \nto start anew. I have experienced many misfortunes in my life, \nwhich have forced me to become stubborn and strong-willed. \nHowever, I’ve managed to stay kind and generous.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Lisbet","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":1800000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557636357,"modifiedTime":1781557636357,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
