{"_id":"BiancaKarenmann2","name":"Bianca Karenmann - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Bianca Karenmann","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I’m a sweet young girl and I just want to live in \npeace. The power of the curse makes me strong and resilient. \nIt also gives me the power to make living beings explode from \nwithin.</p>","notes":"Bloodwhite's Heart - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 117.","positive":"I’m a sweet young girl and I just want to live in \npeace. The power of the curse makes me strong and resilient. \nIt also gives me the power to make living beings explode from \nwithin.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Bianca Karenmann","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":3000000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557628721,"modifiedTime":1781557628721,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"EduardoAndFelipe","name":"Eduardo and Felipe - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Eduardo and Felipe","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>We are two guards who are content to leave \nthinking to other people. We do as we’re told while doing as \nlittle as possible. \nThe Di Bello Family \nHouse\nDescriptor: A large, abandoned villa in the bourgeois \ndistricts of Vigo.</p>","notes":"In Your Eyes, with Your Feet - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 156.","positive":"We are two guards who are content to leave \nthinking to other people. We do as we’re told while doing as \nlittle as possible. \nThe Di Bello Family \nHouse\nDescriptor: A large, abandoned villa in the bourgeois \ndistricts of Vigo.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Eduardo and Felipe","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":3100000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557637071,"modifiedTime":1781557637071,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"SvennTheSkilledH","name":"Svenn the Skilled Hunter - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Svenn the Skilled Hunter","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a skilled huntsman and I boast of all the \nprey I have bagged in my long career. I’m a man of the world \nand I’m used to handling every situation without too many \nscruples.</p>","notes":"Bloodwhite's Heart - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 113.","positive":"I am a skilled huntsman and I boast of all the \nprey I have bagged in my long career. I’m a man of the world \nand I’m used to handling every situation without too many \nscruples.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Svenn the Skilled Hunter","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":3200000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557628565,"modifiedTime":1781557628565,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"AlexandraTheMoth","name":"Alexandra the Mother - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Alexandra the Mother","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a monster, deformed in body and mind. \nThe curse that keeps me alive means that I cannot forget \nwhat I have done. Now, with my misshapen mouth, I can \nonly grunt and whine, preventing me from imploring the \nforgiveness of my daughter.</p>","notes":"Stegeborg's Quiet - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 142.","positive":"I am a monster, deformed in body and mind. \nThe curse that keeps me alive means that I cannot forget \nwhat I have done. Now, with my misshapen mouth, I can \nonly grunt and whine, preventing me from imploring the \nforgiveness of my daughter.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Alexandra the Mother","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":3300000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557636337,"modifiedTime":1781557636337,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
