{"_id":"TheQuietGuards48","name":"The Quiet Guards - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Quiet Guards","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>We are the poor inhabitants of the village, fused \nwith some of the castle’s furnishings. Our transformations \nhave driven us to madness and we blindly obey the will of \nTalia.</p>","notes":"Stegeborg's Quiet - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 138.","positive":"We are the poor inhabitants of the village, fused \nwith some of the castle’s furnishings. Our transformations \nhave driven us to madness and we blindly obey the will of \nTalia.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Quiet Guards","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":4900000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557636197,"modifiedTime":1781557636197,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"BerendTheCrazedC","name":"Berend the Crazed Captain - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Berend the Crazed Captain","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I am the captain of the previous expedition \nand the only one left of my crew. I learned to survive by \nmasking my smell with the stench of rotten fish.</p>","notes":"Hunger Island - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 98.","positive":"I am the captain of the previous expedition \nand the only one left of my crew. I learned to survive by \nmasking my smell with the stench of rotten fish.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Berend the Crazed Captain","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":5000000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557626341,"modifiedTime":1781557626341,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Sailors50xxxxxxx","name":"Sailors - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sailors","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>We are sailors under Captain Arne’s orders. We \nare skilled sea wolves, more comfortable at sea than on land.</p>","notes":"Hunger Island - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 95.","positive":"We are sailors under Captain Arne’s orders. We \nare skilled sea wolves, more comfortable at sea than on land.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Sailors","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":5100000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557626239,"modifiedTime":1781557626239,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"JoannaCalledNana","name":"Joanna called Nana the Servant - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Joanna called Nana the Servant","sourcePack":"broken-ones-actors"}},"system":{"description":"<p>I have been Lady Gwendolyn’s trusted personal \nservant for over ten years. I saw the young heir grow up and I \nam as fond of her as if she were my own daughter.</p>","notes":"I Don't Believe - bt-tbo-1-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, page 84.","positive":"I have been Lady Gwendolyn’s trusted personal \nservant for over ten years. I saw the young heir grow up and I \nam as fond of her as if she were my own daughter.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Joanna called Nana the Servant","category":"threat","source":"The Broken Ones"},"sort":5200000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557625638,"modifiedTime":1781557625638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
